<view class="container">
  <view class="profile-card card">
    <view class="profile-main">
      <image class="avatar" src="{{userInfo.avatarUrl}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
      <view class="profile-info">
        <view class="nickname">{{userInfo.nickName}}</view>
        <view class="sync-badge">
          <text class="sync-dot"></text>
          <text class="sync-text">{{syncStatus}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="cloud-intro">
      全平台无缝同步，支持微信跨设备登录随时查看历史记录。数据本地与云端全面安全加密，时刻贴心守护您的身体机密隐私。
    </view>
    <view class="profile-actions">
      <view class="action-btn" wx:if="{{!isLoggedIn}}" bindtap="openLoginModal" hover-class="action-btn-hover">🔑 登录/注册</view>
      <view class="action-btn action-logout" wx:if="{{isLoggedIn}}" bindtap="handleLogout" hover-class="action-btn-hover">🚪 退出登录</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="science-entry card" bindtap="openScience">
    <view class="science-entry-left">
      <view class="science-icon">💡</view>
      <view class="science-info">
        <view class="science-title">布里斯托分类科普</view>
        <view class="science-desc">如何读懂便便性状传递的肠壁信号？</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="science-arrow">查看</view>
  </view>

  <view class="menu-list card">
    <view class="menu-item" bindtap="goToLeaderboard" hover-class="menu-item-hover">
      <view class="menu-left">
        <text class="menu-icon">🏆</text>
        <text class="menu-text">拉翔排行榜</text>
      </view>
      <text class="menu-arrow">▶</text>
    </view>

    <button class="menu-item feedback-btn" open-type="feedback" hover-class="menu-item-hover">
      <view class="menu-left">
        <text class="menu-icon">💬</text>
        <text class="menu-text">产品槽点反馈</text>
      </view>
      <text class="menu-arrow">▶</text>
    </button>

    <button class="menu-item feedback-btn" open-type="contact" hover-class="menu-item-hover">
      <view class="menu-left">
        <text class="menu-icon">📞</text>
        <text class="menu-text">在线客服咨询</text>
      </view>
      <text class="menu-arrow">▶</text>
    </button>

    <view class="menu-item" bindtap="openAbout" hover-class="menu-item-hover">
      <view class="menu-left">
        <text class="menu-icon">💚</text>
        <text class="menu-text">关于拉个翔</text>
      </view>
      <text class="menu-arrow">▶</text>
    </view>

    <view class="menu-item" bindtap="clearCache" hover-class="menu-item-hover">
      <view class="menu-left">
        <text class="menu-icon text-red">🗑️</text>
        <text class="menu-text text-red">清空本地所有缓存</text>
      </view>
      <text class="menu-arrow">▶</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="modal-mask" wx:if="{{showLoginModal}}" bindtap="closeLoginModal">
    <view class="modal-box login-modal" catchtap="none">
      <view class="modal-header">
        <view class="modal-title">👤 设置个人资料</view>
        <view class="modal-close" bindtap="closeLoginModal">×</view>
      </view>
      <view class="login-form">
        <view class="avatar-section">
          <image class="preview-avatar" src="{{tempAvatarUrl}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        </view>
        <view class="avatar-btns">
          <button class="wx-avatar-btn" open-type="chooseAvatar" bindchooseavatar="onChooseAvatar">
            <view class="avatar-btn-row">
              <text class="avatar-btn-icon">💬</text>
              <text class="avatar-btn-label">微信头像</text>
            </view>
          </button>
          <button class="custom-avatar-btn" bindtap="onChooseCustomAvatar">
            <view class="avatar-btn-row">
              <text class="avatar-btn-icon">📷</text>
              <text class="avatar-btn-label">本地上传</text>
            </view>
          </button>
        </view>
        <view class="nickname-section">
          <view class="input-label">昵称</view>
          <input
            class="nickname-input"
            type="nickname"
            placeholder="请输入你的昵称"
            value="{{tempNickName}}"
            bindinput="onNicknameInput"
            bindblur="onNicknameBlur"
            maxlength="20"
          />
        </view>
        <button class="login-confirm-btn" bindtap="confirmLogin">确认保存</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="modal-mask" wx:if="{{showScience}}" bindtap="closeScience">
    <view class="modal-box science-modal" catchtap="none">
      <view class="modal-header">
        <view class="modal-title">📖 布里斯托分类法解读</view>
        <view class="modal-close" bindtap="closeScience">×</view>
      </view>
      <scroll-view class="modal-scroll" scroll-y="true">
        <view class="science-item-card" wx:for="{{scienceList}}" wx:key="type">
          <view class="sci-title-row">
            <text class="sci-type-badge">{{item.type}}型</text>
            <text class="sci-name">{{item.name}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="sci-status">{{item.subtitle}}</view>
          <view class="sci-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
        </view>
      </scroll-view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="modal-mask" wx:if="{{showAbout}}" bindtap="closeAbout">
    <view class="modal-box about-modal" catchtap="none">
      <view class="modal-header">
        <view class="modal-title">💚 关于拉个翔</view>
        <view class="modal-close" bindtap="closeAbout">×</view>
      </view>
      <view class="about-content">
        <image class="about-logo-img" src="/images/logo.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
        <view class="about-name">拉个翔 v1.0.0</view>
        <view class="about-desc">
          致力于为每一位用户提供干净、温馨、无负担的排便追踪与习惯纠正工具。遵循布里斯托大便医学标准，充当您随身的健康消化顾问。
        </view>
        <view class="about-footer">拉个翔设计开发团队 · 温暖呈献 @ 2026</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
